		<h2>Follow the instructions to build your app:</h2>
		   <ol>1. If you don't have a Cloudfoundry account create at <a href=http://www.cloudfoundry.com/>cloudfoundry.com</a></ol>
		   <ol>>>1.a.  Create a stub application on Cloudfoundry, record the application FQDN</ol>
           <ol>2. Create a new app on <a href=https://developers.facebook.com/>facebook</a></ol>
		   <ol>>>2a. Click on the Facebook "new app" button</ol>
		   <ol>>>2b. Enter the name of the Cloudfoundry application created in Step 1 in the domain name (no'http://') </ol>
		   <ol>>>2c. Enter the Cloudfoundry application FQDN in the website field </ol>
           <ol>>>2d. Create the app</ol>
		   <ol>3. Enter the Facebook App ID and App Secret in this form</ol>
		   <ol>4. Submit form and download zip file containing template application</ol>
           <ol>5. Extract zip and publish to Cloudfoundry</ol>
           <ol>>>5a. vmc update and bind to rabbitmq service</ol>
           <ol>Congratulations, your app is now running!</ol>
